\\ G.f.: Sum_{j>=1} q^(4*j)*(1-q^(3*j))*(1-q^(9*j))/((1-q^j)*(1-q^(3*j))) * Product_{k=j+1..3*j-1} (1-q^(4*k))/(1-q^k).
